ship 12+ months required?","a":"Cohabitation or qualifying exception"},{"q":"Is Relationship evidence package required?","a":"Relationship evidence package is typically required."},{"q":"Is Health requirements required?","a":"Assess whether Health requirements is satisfied for this case."},{"q":"Is Character requirements (police certs) required?","a":"Assess whether Character requirements (police certs) is satisfied for this case."},{"q":"Is Partner support declaration required?","a":"Partner support declaration is typically required."},{"q":"Is Immigration history disclosed required?","a":"Immigration history disclosed is typically required."},{"q":"What is the Processing time?","a":"8–16w — Partnership resident"},{"q":"What is the Government fee?","a":"NZD $1,670 — Approx online fee"},{"q":"What is the Our approval rate?","a":"88% — ~79% benchmark"},{"q":"What is the Required docs?","a":"19 — + relationship evidence"},{"q":"What is the Consultancy fee?","a":"See fee tab — + govt & medical"},{"q":"What if the client has Insufficient cohabitation evidence?","a":"Joint lease, bills, photos with dates, affidavits"},{"q":"Why is Insufficient cohabitation evidence a problem?","a":"Cannot prove 12+ months living together."},{"q":"What if the client has Weak relationship timeline?","a":"Chronological narrative; visit records; family statements"},{"q":"Why is Weak relationship timeline a problem?","a":"Few photos, no communication history, recent relationship."}]'::jsonb
